flowchart TD
    subgraph Field[Field Devices]
        Modbus[Modbus RTU\nRS-485 sensors]
        OPCUA[OPC-UA\nIndustrial PLC]
        MQTT[MQTT Wi-Fi\nSmart sensors]
        LoRa[LoRaWAN\nBattery nodes]
    end

    subgraph GW[IoT Gateway]
        ModbusAdapt[Modbus adapter]
        OPCAdapt[OPC-UA adapter]
        MQTTAdapt[MQTT adapter]
        LoRaAdapt[LoRaWAN adapter]
        Bus[Internal message bus\nCanonical JSON format]
        Processing[Local processing engine\nFilter / enrich / downsample]
        Shadow[Local device shadow\nLast-known state store]
        Queue[Outbound queue\nPersistent at-least-once]
        DevMgmt[Device management\nProvisioning / config]
    end

    Modbus --> ModbusAdapt
    OPCUA --> OPCAdapt
    MQTT --> MQTTAdapt
    LoRa --> LoRaAdapt

    ModbusAdapt --> Bus
    OPCAdapt --> Bus
    MQTTAdapt --> Bus
    LoRaAdapt --> Bus

    Bus --> Processing
    Processing --> Shadow
    Processing --> Queue
    Queue --> Uplink[Cloud uplink\nMQTT-TLS / HTTPS]
    Uplink --> Cloud[Cloud IoT Platform]
    Cloud --> DevMgmt
